      <description>Your pets are not going to be effective in PvP. Yes, toys will help. They will not solve the problem, though.&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Do not dire charm in PvP. It will be dispelled. Giving your pet&#xD;
PvP-procing weapons (snare, blind, etc.) can help but is only really an&#xD;
option if you're fairly plat-rich.&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
Think of a subtle, balance-minded way to improve the pets for PvP and post it on this board for discussion, IMHO.&lt;br&gt;&#xD;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
